data.description: This beautiful 2 bedroom 1 and a 1/2 bathroom condominium is waiting for a new owner in beautiful Clearwater Florida. The properties downstairs consists of a living room, dining room, half bathroom, and kitchen. Upstairs has a full bathroom with two bedrooms. Property has an attached two car garage, which is shared with another unit. Additionally there is one assigned parking space for the unit and plenty of visitor spaces. Community has many amenities including pool, tennis courts, and private path leading to a peaceful fishing pier. Property is closely located to all the amenities Tampa Bay has to offer. Seller will provide a credit for upstairs flooring and stairs.
